game_description: In this game called "Frog Flyers" you bounce around with friends and play minigames. There is also parkour to do with friends. Hope you enjoy Frog Flyers! Trust me you will have so much fun playing Frog Flyers. it's one of the best games out there's with added cosmetics and names and minigames. Go Check Out Frog Flyers. GO TO FrogFlyers.com to see more
review_1: This such a good game. The map in my opinion has to be paintball map with real shooting mechanics you should really try this game out
review_2: I'm the original owner of this game Frog Flyers, back from May of last year. Game was stolen by RandomVideos, he never had the project and tried recreating everything but never could. Game got worse and worse then he attacked me while I was building an even better game called RoboRun. Try it out on AppLab and you'll see what Frog Flyers was meant to be. Thanks
